Java kernel hints for z-sandbox

Context to load immediately
@build.gradle

Scope
- High-precision kernels live here. Use BigDecimal for precision-critical math; BigInteger for integer ops.

Standards
- Keep methods pure and testable. Throw IllegalArgumentException for invalid inputs (n ≤ 0). Log approximations.
- Maintain invariants and precision. Add JUnit tests in src/test/java and run via ./gradlew test.
- Prefer efficient search strategies; avoid naive O(N) scans in production paths. Use streams sparingly in hot paths.

Build & Test
- ./gradlew build && ./gradlew test (must pass before PRs).

Interop
- Exchange data via CSV with python/; document schema in docs/.
